2. Added probability calibration for SVM to produce reliable probability estimates for risk prediction.
3. Developed a transformer-based deep learning model using DistilBERT with validation monitoring and automatic best model selection.
4. Integrated comprehensive evaluation metrics including Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1-score, and ROC analysis for model performance assessment.
5. Performed extensive exploratory data analysis (EDA) including statistical summaries, feature correlations, and data visualization.
6. Implemented hyperparameter tuning using RandomizedSearchCV to optimize model performance and improve prediction accuracy.
7. Developed prediction and explanation functions, model saving mechanisms, and performance visualization plots for deployment-ready risk detection.
